snippet.title: DEVIATOR Early Access Release Trailer - Available on Steam on August 2nd!
snippet.description:
DEVIATOR Early Access Release on August 2, 2024!

Standard Edition: $6.99
Deluxe Edition: $9.99 (includes soundtrack)

There will be a 10% launch discount in the first 2 weeks!

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2620730/_/
